{
  "stem": "1033.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Of course, I always did what I was told.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I never saw [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Farcash ?] again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he did manage to get back to Budapest because when I got back myself, I talked to people, and they told me that, yeah, he did come back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so we got to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was a large camp, a precinct, perhaps a four-story red brick building in which, by the time I got there, there were hundreds, maybe 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Some with kids, some with belongings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Some had suitcases.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we just lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We just waited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were barricaded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Nobody could move out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were no countings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Like later on, we had to line up and to be counted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this was mid-summer, 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And around the tenth of August of '44.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later, I learned that this was the last transport, official transport, from Hungary into Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the 10th of August, the bells were ringing, and we were asked to line up in front of the precinct.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I always wanted to escape, so I ran up on the top of-- it was a flat roof.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I ran on top of the roof.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I could see the people shouting, calling to one another, lining up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was crouched behind a chimney.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the chimney covered me from the door leading up to the roof.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as I was there watching and observing, suddenly I heard the door open.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as the man looked at me, I looked at him, and we saw each other at the same time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a man  off-- a young man, maybe 30, in a black leather jacket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Shiny black hair slunk onto his skull.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
